extends ../templates/base
block vars
  - var title = "Approach"
block approach
  .approach
    .approach-bg
      .approach__inner
        h2.approach__title Our Approach
        p.approach__text Our process is highly iterative and focused on the needs of your business and its customers. Technology exists for the people who use it, and we never forget that.
    .container
      .approach__service
        .approach__box
          .approach__box-icon
            include ../../img/approach_1.svg
          h2.approach__box-title Pleased to Meet You
          p.approach__box-text Your vision matters most, and we want to learn  about it while getting to know you and your business needs. We are not faceless mercenaries, but a talented team of developers & designers that wants to help you succeed. 
        .approach__box
          .approach__box-icon
            include ../../img/approach_2.svg
          h2.approach__box-title Planning Session
          p.approach__box-text Furious whiteboarding and challenged ideas will lead to a sketch of your idea while generating a set of user stories, which are your entire application in written form. We will use these to prioritize your needs, estimate your cost and get cracking on the code. 
        .approach__box
          .approach__box-icon
            include ../../img/approach_3.svg
          h2.approach__box-title Design
          p.approach__box-text Design is where form and function meet. Tools are only as powerful as one’s ability to use them, and we will work together to design intuitive, powerfully simple applications. Our designers are artists, and our developers are craftsmen. Your software will look as good as it feels.
        .approach__box
          .approach__box-icon
            include ../../img/approach_4.svg
          h2.approach__box-title Minimum Viable Product
          p.approach__box-text Everything comes together in your Minimum Viable Product. We will get this into the hands of users in order to learn from their interactions and the data they generate. This saves you money by taking the guesswork out of development. We will crunch the numbers and sweat the technical details to keep you on the path to profitability.
        .approach__box
          .approach__box-icon
            include ../../img/approach_5.svg
          h2.approach__box-title Iterate
          p.approach__box-text You have users, revenue and an appetite for more. Lessons learned will be turned into improved functionality and a better, stronger application, capturing more users along the way. Perhaps you are ready to hire your own tech team, and we will proudly hand you off like parents at the first day of school…but you will always have a room in our home.
block digital
  h2.digital__title Our Digital Expertise
  .digital__wrap
    .digital__box
      h3.digital__type Web Applications
      p.digital__desc If your business is on the web then we can help build it or make it better.
    .digital__box
      h3.digital__type Mobile Applications
      p.digital__desc Customers are on the go, and so is their technology. We make software that is as mobile as the people who use it.
    .digital__box
      h3.digital__type Scalability
      p.digital__desc Growing pains mean traction, but they don't have to hurt. You can't afford to lose customers due to poorly implemented code, and we won't let you.
    .digital__box
      h3.digital__type Testing
      p.digital__desc Stories are nice, but learning through data is what creates a great product and a sustainable business. We track, analyze and learn as we build simply perfect software.
    .digital__box
      h3.digital__type Lean Tactics
      p.digital__desc Lean tactics ensure we build the right application, every time, by adapting to new information gleaned through user interactions.
    .digital__box
      h3.digital__type Agile Methodologies
      p.digital__desc We will work together to uncover the most pressing needs of your users before writing one line of code, and ensure our work serves the end goal, not to project plan as dictated on day one.
  .digital__start
    h2.digital__type.digital__start-title Want to start the conversation?
    button.btn.digital__start-btn Contact Us


